[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到誰讓他煉器的！第二章，第三集，三人成虎。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "低語洞窟任務完成後，滄溟子的殘魂正式成為邏輯修正小組的「名譽顧問」。長老派了第二個任務：修復後山崩塌的藏經閣。三百年沒有人去過的藏經閣，書的怨念太重，把建築都震塌了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "長老召集邏輯修正小組，說明了任務內容。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "藏經閣三年前因為結構老化崩塌了。裡面的書籍至今沒有人整理。你們去修復一下。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "長老，藏經閣為什麼會自己崩塌？"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三百年沒人去過。書的怨念太重，把建築震塌了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……書會有怨念？"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你試試三百年沒有人翻開你寫的論文。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……長老這句話比我的論文還殘忍。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "藏經閣。三百年沒人維護的資訊系統。典型的「缺乏使用者回饋導致系統退化」。我對這個任務很有興趣。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨，我警告你，不許把藏經閣改成什麼奇怪的東西。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "放心，長老。我只是去做系統維護。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "每次周墨說「放心」，我就開始擔心。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三人來到藏經閣廢墟。剛踏進門，一本書從空中飛來——"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "什麼——！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "書本直接搶走了陸陽口袋裡的投降表，然後開始朗讀。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那是我的投降表！那是我精心設計的！裡面有十七種投降姿勢的插圖！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "另一本書飛向孟景舟，搶走了他的論文草稿。幾秒後，書上多了一堆紅筆批改。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等等……這本書在批改我的論文？它加了一行：「論點不成立，建議重寫」——還畫了一個大大的叉。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "有趣。這些書的攻擊行為，本質上是「尋求關注」。三百年沒有人閱讀它們，它們的防禦機制是對「被忽視」的反應。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "所以你的意思是……這些書在鬧脾氣？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "從工程學的角度來說，這是一個「缺乏正向回饋的系統」。解決方案很簡單——給它們「點讚」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨掏出一個小裝置，對著每本書按了一下。書們立刻安靜了下來。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "就……就這樣？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我給每本書加了一個「認可系統」。它們得到了三百年來第一個正向評價。問題解決。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "但是周墨……藏經閣裡所有的書都在看著你。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "數百本書同時翻開，書頁發出沙沙聲，仿佛在說——「我的呢？」"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……我來給它們加一個「自動評價系統」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三天後。藏經閣裡的書開始互相寫評論。一本《劍道入門》給自己打了五星，評語是「本世紀最偉大的著作」。旁邊的《煉丹基礎》不甘示弱，寫了一篇長文評論自己「超越了上古大能」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨，你的自動評價系統出了問題。這些書的文學水平直線下降——它們現在只會互相吹捧。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "啊……我忘記加「評價標準」了。沒有標準的評價系統，就像沒有尺的裁縫——"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "會把衣服做成正方形。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……我本來想說「會亂剪一氣」，但你的比喻更好。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "OutroScene",
    "file": "04-outro.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "感謝收看誰讓他煉器的！第二章第三集，三人成虎。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "邏輯修正小組成功「修復」了藏經閣——雖然現在裡面的書都在互相吹捧，文學水平跌到了谷底。周墨的自動評價系統效率很高，但忘了加評價標準，導致藏經閣成了修仙界最大的「假評價工廠」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "下集預告：長老派邏輯修正小組參加五年一次的宗門秘境探索。別家宗門在認真破解上古禁制，周墨掏出了「雷射切割陣法」——效率很高，但把整座秘境的禁制全切斷了，觸發了自毀倒數。"
      }
    ]
  }
]
